{"id": "1404268225679720590", "channel_id": "1404268225679720590", "type": 0, "author_id": "452609886170251265", "author_name": "tksn.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Even though some older limited characters have been added to the standard banner, the rates are so low that pulling them is unreasonable and cannot be guaranteed. Limited wheels are even worse since you cannot target a specific realm. I joined a month ago during the self-select event awakening banner (自選活動喚醒：久遠的呼喚) where you could choose a rate-up limited character and weapon, and it was very helpful for me when starting out. I have convinced some friends to start playing the game recently, but they do not have access to that banner and many of them are missing limited characters that can help out a lot with their teambuilding and progression. \n\nPlease consider running the self-select event awakening banner more often. I think it is a big help to newer players since it gives them access to characters they cannot get otherwise. I think older players might not care as much about these select banners since the rate is not as good as the usual limited character/wheel banners, but for newer players they are very helpful and many of my friends would appreciate a self-select banner when starting out.", "timestamp": "2025-08-11T01:00:35.044000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "⬆️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1404268225679720590", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please do more [Self-Select Event Awakening] banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
